  "description": "Express your endless love with this exquisite Cross Eternity Moissanite wedding ring. Crafted from S925 sterling silver with a sleek white gold finish, this ring features two delicate rows of sparkling D-color, VVS1 Moissanite stones, totaling 0.10 carats. The stones gradually increase in size towards the center, where a single Moissanite stone shines between the two rows, symbolizing unity and togetherness.\n\nThe inner band is engraved with “S925” and “0.10CT,” ensuring both quality and authenticity.\n\nKey Features:\n\nCross Eternity Design: A unique and modern symbol of infinite love.\n\nHigh-Quality Moissanite Stones: D-color, VVS1 clarity stones totaling 0.10 carats, arranged to enhance sparkle.\n\nS925 Sterling Silver: Durable and hypoallergenic, plated in white gold for a polished look.\n\nAuthenticity Markings: Engraved with \"S925\" and \"0.10CT\" for quality assurance.\n\nCelebrate a bond that lasts forever with this refined and meaningful piece.\n\nMaterial: 925 Sterling Silver\n\nCarat Weight: 0.07ct\n\nColor Grade : D\n\nClarity Grade: VVS1\n\nCut Grade: Excellent",
